entry.title: sourcelocation/DebToIPA
entry.summary:
Convert .deb apps to .ipa files, on iOS, locally

DebtoIPA

Convert .deb apps to .ipa files, on iOS, locally

Usage

  1. Download .deb that contains .app file. You will get an error if you try importing other files.
  2. Open Deb to IPA
  3. Tap on import
  4. Select .deb
  5. Wait
  6. Open in TrollStore (captured on simulator, so TrollStore isn't installed)
  7. ⭐️ this project if you find it usefull :)
